You are working on an ESP32-P4 / LVGL 9 touch-screen virtual gamepad firmware repository.

Read these files before editing:
- AGENTS.md
- docs/PROJECT_MAP.md
- docs/VALIDATION.md
- docs/SETUP_WINDOWS.md
- docs/HARDWARE.md

Main firmware project:
- lvgl_demo_v9/

Build command:
cd lvgl_demo_v9
idf.py set-target esp32p4
idf.py build

Important rules:
- Do not remove local component overrides under lvgl_demo_v9/components/.
- Do not commit build directories, managed_components, logs, or local IDE files.
- Preserve the GT911 multi-touch bridge; LVGL single-pointer input alone is not enough for this gamepad.
- Keep lvgl_demo_v9 inside the repository root because main/CMakeLists.txt references ../../src.
- Update README/docs when setup, build, hardware, or architecture changes.
- Verify with idf.py build before claiming firmware success.
